Discussion list
---------------

*aio-libs* google group: https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/aio-libs

Requirements
------------

- Python >= 3.4.1
- chardet https://pypi.python.org/pypi/chardet

Optionally you may install cChardet library:
https://pypi.python.org/pypi/cchardet/1.0.0


